    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >就这么个情况：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像样的武器没有，不过你能让松鼠当枪喷坚果，还能抡起小板凳猛砸，把毛绒入侵者撕个稀巴烂！管不管用？不好说。好不好看？绝对炸场！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/0507de5b8b19fed2ab4155a41b7f6c84.poster.avif?t=1772209252\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/0507de5b8b19fed2ab4155a41b7f6c84.webm?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/0507de5b8b19fed2ab4155a41b7f6c84.mp4?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >屠杀开始了！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看这帮毛绒渣子者当场崩成碎片，是每个小凶灵猎手的私密快感。你能把入侵者撕成多少块？要是到现在还打不出小凶灵的填充棉，就别叫自己小凶灵猎手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/5272fba47196297fe93c0c623064550e.poster.avif?t=1772209252\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/5272fba47196297fe93c0c623064550e.webm?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/5272fba47196297fe93c0c623064550e.mp4?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽情狂欢，仿佛没有明天！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >末日当头，你分到的助手是最离谱的那个。他不懂什么叫恐惧，也不懂什么叫羞耻。老实说，还挺笨的。可一旦被你好好升级，他就能喷火又喷冰，对付小凶灵时无人能敌！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/ecd2280b7ac8d65bc7d959e1dfc472a4.poster.avif?t=1772209252\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/ecd2280b7ac8d65bc7d959e1dfc472a4.webm?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297800/extras/ecd2280b7ac8d65bc7d959e1dfc472a4.mp4?t=1772209252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>离谱但真好使的武器</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用最离谱的武器，让敌人吃到尴尬伤害加成！脏拖把？绝了！隔夜法棍？妙！香肠机枪？给我整俩！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>理想的鸽子搭档</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >末日里的最差搭档，既没脑子也没良心。不过他会喷火，还能把敌人冻住。来认识一下会说话的鸽子，他既是你最忠实的粉丝，也是个十足的麻烦精。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挨打就当场碎裂的敌人</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怎么确认小凶灵已经死透？把它撕成碎片。把每一道缝线挑开，让填充棉漫天飞。把它里外翻个遍。合成纤维的肠子、被扯落的纽扣、被撕成条的毛绒外皮，就是你与敌人说话的语言。</p>",
